{{ 'section-luxury-coming-soon.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
<script src="{{ 'luxury-coming-soon.js' | asset_url }}" defer="defer"></script>

{% comment %}
  Luxury Coming Soon — cinematic, full-bleed "gated drop" landing page
  used as the storefront password page's sole content. Ported from the
  leehaf-batch01-gate reference file (pre-label, symbol mark, wordmark,
  scarcity statement, finality line, 3-state entry interaction, footer
  line), rebuilt on real Dawn conventions.

  Fonts: Cormorant Garamond (display) + Jost (labels/UI) are loaded
  directly from Google Fonts below, scoped to this section only. This
  is self-contained on purpose — it doesn't depend on the theme's
  global type_header_font/type_body_font settings, so it renders
  correctly regardless of what font handle is currently selected
  there.

  The top-right "Enter using password" link reuses Dawn's real
  password-modal.js / details-modal.js custom elements and the native
  storefront_password form tag — both scripts are already loaded
  globally by layout/password.liquid, and the exact password-modal /
  details / summary / button(type=button) structure below is required
  for that JS to find and wire up correctly.

  The entry-zone below the finality line is the real, working
  pre-launch signup: a genuine "form 'customer'" tag that creates
  an actual Shopify customer record tagged "pre-launch" on submit.
  Unlike the reference file's fake fetch('YOUR_ENDPOINT_URL') +
  setTimeout demo, this submits for real via a normal full-page
  form post. JS only handles the button -> input reveal (state 1 -> 2)
  client-side, exactly like the reference; the input -> success
  transition (state 2 -> 3) happens for real, server-side, driven by
  Shopify's own form.posted_successfully? / form.errors on reload.
{% endcomment %}

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link
  href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300&family=Jost:wght@200;300;400;500&display=swap"
  rel="stylesheet"
>

{%- liquid
  assign video = section.settings.background_video
  assign image = section.settings.background_image
  assign pre_label = section.settings.pre_label
  assign headline = section.settings.headline
  assign scarcity_statement = section.settings.scarcity_statement
  assign finality_line = section.settings.finality_line
  assign button_label = section.settings.button_label | default: 'Request Entry'
  assign success_message = section.settings.success_message
  assign footer_left = section.settings.footer_left
  assign footer_right = section.settings.footer_right

  if form.posted_successfully?
    assign entry_state = 'success'
  elsif form.errors
    assign entry_state = 'form'
  else
    assign entry_state = 'trigger'
  endif

  capture entry_form_class
    echo 'entry-form'
    if entry_state == 'form'
      echo ' is-active'
    endif
  endcapture

  capture entry_trigger_class
    echo 'entry-trigger'
    if entry_state != 'trigger'
      echo ' is-hidden'
    endif
  endcapture
-%}

<div class="luxury-coming-soon color-{{ section.settings.color_scheme }}" data-luxury-coming-soon>

  <div class="luxury-coming-soon__media" aria-hidden="true">
    {%- if video -%}
      {{
        video
        | video_tag:
          autoplay: true,
          loop: true,
          muted: true,
          controls: false,
          class: 'luxury-coming-soon__video',
          image_size: '1920x'
      }}
    {%- elsif image -%}
      {{
        image
        | image_url: width: 2200
        | image_tag:
          sizes: '100vw',
          widths: '750, 1100, 1500, 1780, 2200, 3000',
          fetchpriority: 'high',
          alt: '',
          class: 'luxury-coming-soon__image'
      }}
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- comment -%}
      No "else" placeholder here on purpose: Shopify's generic gray
      placeholder graphic looks broken/unfinished on a luxury landing
      page. With no video or image set, the navy background-color
      (from the color scheme) plus the overlay and grain below carry
      the whole scene on their own -- deliberate, not missing.
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="luxury-coming-soon__tint"></div>
    <div class="luxury-coming-soon__overlay"></div>
    <div class="luxury-coming-soon__grain"></div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%}
    This is Shopify's native storefront-password login mechanism.
    It's only relevant when this section is rendered on Shopify's own
    templates/password.json (i.e. real store-wide password protection
    is turned on) -- there, a visitor genuinely needs a way to submit
    the store password, and this modal is that form.

    When this same section is used as the plain, ungated homepage
    (templates/index.json), there is nothing to "enter" and no
    password to submit, so this trigger is hidden via the
    show_password_entry setting (defaulted off there). Leaving it on
    in that context was surfacing Shopify's own bot-protection
    (a captcha challenge on the password form) with no valid password
    to actually satisfy it -- a broken, unprofessional dead end for
    visitors, not a bug in this theme's code.
  {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- if section.settings.show_password_entry -%}
    <password-modal class="luxury-coming-soon__password-modal">
      <details class="password-modal modal">
        <summary class="modal__toggle luxury-coming-soon__password-trigger" aria-haspopup="dialog">
          <div class="modal__toggle-open">
            {{ 'general.password_page.login_password_button' | t }}
          </div>
          <div class="modal__toggle-close" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="svg-wrapper">
              {{- 'icon-close.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
            </span>
          </div>
        </summary>
        <div
          class="modal__content"
          role="dialog"
          aria-labelledby="LuxuryComingSoonPasswordHeading"
          aria-modal="true"
        >
          <div class="password-modal__content" tabindex="-1">
            <button type="button" class="modal__close-button link" aria-label="{{ 'accessibility.close' | t }}">
              <span class="svg-wrapper">
                {{- 'icon-close.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
              </span>
            </button>
            <h2 class="password-modal__content-heading" id="LuxuryComingSoonPasswordHeading">
              {{ 'general.password_page.login_form_heading' | t }}
            </h2>
            {%- form 'storefront_password', class: 'password-form' -%}
              <div class="password-field field{% if form.errors %} password-field--error{% endif %}">
                <input
                  type="password"
                  name="password"
                  id="LuxuryComingSoonPassword"
                  class="field__input"
                  autocomplete="current-password"
                  {% if form.errors %}
                    aria-invalid="true"
                    aria-describedby="LuxuryComingSoonPassword-error"
                  {%- endif -%}
                  placeholder="{{ 'general.password_page.login_form_password_placeholder' | t }}"
                >
                <label class="field__label" for="LuxuryComingSoonPassword">
                  {{- 'general.password_page.login_form_password_placeholder' | t -}}
                </label>
                {%- if form.errors -%}
                  <div id="LuxuryComingSoonPassword-error" role="status">
                    <span class="visually-hidden">{{ 'accessibility.error' | t }}</span>
                    <span class="form__message">
                      {{ 'general.password_page.login_form_error' | t -}}
                    </span>
                  </div>
                {%- endif -%}
              </div>
              <button name="commit" class="password-button button button--outline">
                {{ 'general.password_page.login_form_submit' | t }}
              </button>
            {%- endform -%}
          </div>
        </div>
      </details>
    </password-modal>
  {%- endif -%}

  <div class="luxury-coming-soon__content">
    <div class="luxury-coming-soon__content-inner">

      {%- if pre_label != blank -%}
        <p class="pre-label">{{ pre_label | escape }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}

      <div class="mark" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 62 62" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M29.37 0.58L0.57 29.18C-0.19 29.94-0.19 31.17 0.57 31.92C1.21 32.55 2.19 32.66 2.95 32.19L38.33 10.15C39.43 9.47 39.60 7.94 38.68 7.03L32.18 0.58C31.40-0.20 30.15-0.20 29.37 0.58Z" fill="#F7F4EE"/>
          <path d="M25.27 37.93L26.16 25.06C26.28 23.43 24.50 22.36 23.12 23.21L5.86 33.87C4.76 34.55 4.58 36.08 5.50 36.99L24.05 55.41L29.37 60.77C30.15 61.55 31.41 61.56 32.19 60.78L47.07 46.14C48.12 45.11 47.73 43.34 46.35 42.84L27.94 36.19C26.69 35.74 25.36 36.61 25.27 37.93Z" fill="#F7F4EE"/>
          <path d="M28.10 31.89L28.84 21.13C28.88 20.51 29.21 19.95 29.72 19.61L41.25 11.93C42.04 11.40 43.09 11.50 43.77 12.18L60.79 29.16C61.57 29.93 61.58 31.18 60.82 31.97L51.95 41.11C51.40 41.68 50.55 41.87 49.81 41.59L29.39 33.89C28.57 33.58 28.04 32.77 28.10 31.89Z" fill="#F7F4EE"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      {%- if headline != blank -%}
        <h1 class="wordmark">{{ headline | escape }}</h1>
      {%- endif -%}

      <div class="rule"></div>

      {%- if scarcity_statement != blank -%}
        <p class="scarcity">{{ scarcity_statement | escape }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if finality_line != blank -%}
        <p class="scarcity-finality">{{ finality_line | escape }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}

      <div class="entry-zone" data-entry-zone data-initial-state="{{ entry_state }}">

        <button type="button" class="{{ entry_trigger_class }}" data-entry-trigger>
          {{ button_label | escape }}
        </button>

        {%- form 'customer', id: 'LuxuryComingSoonForm', class: entry_form_class -%}
          <input type="hidden" name="contact[tags]" value="pre-launch">
          <div class="entry-form-field">
            <input
              type="email"
              id="LuxuryComingSoonForm-email"
              name="contact[email]"
              class="entry-input"
              value="{{ form.email }}"
              placeholder="{{ 'luxury_coming_soon.email_placeholder' | t }}"
              aria-label="{{ 'newsletter.label' | t }}"
              required
              autocorrect="off"
              autocapitalize="off"
              autocomplete="email"
              data-entry-input
              {% if form.errors %}
                autofocus
                aria-invalid="true"
                aria-describedby="LuxuryComingSoonForm-email-error"
              {% endif %}
            >
            <span class="entry-line"></span>
          </div>

          {%- if form.errors -%}
            <p class="entry-error" id="LuxuryComingSoonForm-email-error" role="status">
              {{ form.errors.translated_fields.email | capitalize }} {{ form.errors.messages.email }}
            </p>
          {%- endif -%}
        {%- endform -%}

        <div class="entry-success{% if entry_state == 'success' %} is-active{% endif %}" data-entry-success>
          <p class="entry-success-text" role="status" tabindex="-1">
            {{ success_message | escape }}
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  {%- if footer_left != blank or footer_right != blank -%}
    <div class="footline">
      {%- if footer_left != blank -%}
        <span>{{ footer_left | escape }}</span>
      {%- endif -%}
      {%- if footer_left != blank and footer_right != blank -%}
        <div class="dot"></div>
      {%- endif -%}
      {%- if footer_right != blank -%}
        <span>{{ footer_right | escape }}</span>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "t:sections.luxury-coming-soon.name",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "video",
      "id": "background_video",
      "label": "t:sections.luxury-coming-soon.settings.background_video.label"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "background_image",
      "label": "t:sections.luxury-coming-soon.settings.background_image.label"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_password_entry",
      "label": "t:sections.luxury-coming-soon.settings.show_password_entry.label",
      "info": "t:sections.luxury-coming-soon.settings.show_password_entry.info",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "pre_label",
      "label": "t:sections.luxury-coming-soon.settings.pre_label.label",
      "default": "Drop 01 · The Signature Collection"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "headline",
      "label": "t:sections.luxury-coming-soon.settings.headline.label",
      "default": "Leehaf"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "scarcity_statement",
      "label": "t:sections.luxury-coming-soon.settings.scarcity_statement.label",
      "default": "Batch 01. Forty Numbered Sets."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "finality_line",
      "label": "t:sections.luxury-coming-soon.settings.finality_line.label",
      "default": "When the forty are claimed, the archive closes. There will not be a second run."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "button_label",
      "label": "t:sections.luxury-coming-soon.settings.button_label.label",
      "default": "Request Entry"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "success_message",
      "label": "t:sections.luxury-coming-soon.settings.success_message.label",
      "default": "Access secured. The archive awaits."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "footer_left",
      "label": "t:sections.luxury-coming-soon.settings.footer_left.label",
      "default": "Crafted in the Nile Delta"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "footer_right",
      "label": "t:sections.luxury-coming-soon.settings.footer_right.label",
      "default": "Refined in the UK"
    },
    {
      "type": "color_scheme",
      "id": "color_scheme",
      "label": "t:sections.all.colors.label",
      "default": "scheme-4"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
